{"title":"侄女","authors":["刘明达"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"侄女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘明达"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记忆里村子是位瘪嘴奶奶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在爷爷坟前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定格为一幅枯瘦的铁画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天奶奶鬓角插上红花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古老的村子还童了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝙蝠衫在乡亲眼里飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天莽莽撞撞像个小伙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚柔思如缕才像自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四合院圈不住高跟鞋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砖瓦房圆不了风流梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人拴住心早飞了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖着土地的绳索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村外泥土小路竖着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竖一架百步云梯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一本本教科书丰腴童年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张张准考证辉耀青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊角辫散成披肩发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里曳回一朵五彩云"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}